NameFlagsCard.TypeDescription & Constraints
Extension 0..*ExtensionInsight
path 0..*stringPath to the FHIR element that the insight pertains to.
URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/path
insightId 0..1IdentifierID for the insight as known by the source (or source system) that this insight was provided from
URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/insight-id
sourceId 0..1IdentifierThe ID of the source of the insight, such as an individual, algorithm, etc. that generated the insight.
URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/source-id
detected 0..1dateTimeWhen the insight evaluation occurred
URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/detected
category 0..1CodeableConceptTop level category classifying the type of insight, such as Natural Language Processing, Data Quality, etc.
URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/category
valueCodeableConcept 0..1CodeableConceptValue of extension
Binding: Insight Category ValueSet (example)
insightType 0..1CodeableConceptCode for the specific insight type
URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/insight-type
insightDetail 0..*(Complex)Information leveraged to produce the insight results and information specific scoring breakdown when appropriate
URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/insight-detail
result 0..*(Complex)Value specific final insight results
URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/insight-result-summary
url 1..1uri"http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/insight"
value[x] 0..0
